---
import BgGrid from "@/components/assets/BgGrid.astro";
---

<section id="about" class="border-b border-white/10 bg-[#0a0a0a] overflow-hidden">
  <div class="p-8 md:p-16 relative">
    <BgGrid />
    
    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-5xl">
      <p class="text-[#ff5f1f] font-mono text-[10px] mb-12 tracking-[0.4em] uppercase opacity-60">
        // More About me
      </p>
      
      <div class="space-y-8">
        <p class="text-white text-xl md:text-3xl font-bold uppercase tracking-tight leading-tight">
          I am Desmond Achusi, a Nigeria-based ICT specialist and cybersecurity analyst working with NNPC Gas Marketing Limited. I build practical security systems that improve visibility, automate monitoring, and strengthen enterprise defenses from the ground up.
        </p>

        <p class="text-white/50 text-lg md:text-xl uppercase tracking-wide leading-relaxed">
          I work on detection engineering and security automation, designing SOC-style pipelines that turn raw operational data into real, actionable insights. I am hands-on, grounded, and focused on tools that reflect how security operations actually work.
        </p>

        <p class="text-[#ff5f1f] text-lg md:text-xl font-bold uppercase tracking-tighter">
          My goal is to bring this practical expertise to international cybersecurity teams working on detection engineering and resilient infrastructure.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>